  <p>Get started with Adobe Campaign by consulting our intuitive step-by-step guides.</p> 
  <ul>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_GettingStartedEmail.html">Creating a personalized email</a>: create and send personalized emails to a targeted audience.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_GettingStartedLandingPages.html">Offering a subscription to a service</a>: create a subscription to a newsletter using a landing page.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_CreateLandingPage.html">Creating a landing page</a>: manage your landing page templates and create new landing pages that are ready for use.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_ImportExport.html">Exporting and importing a package of custom resources</a>: export and import a package of custom resources from a development environment to a production environment.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_WorkflowSegmentation.html">Creating a cross-channel message workflow</a>: create a workflow by segmenting a population to send an email delivery and an SMS delivery.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_AEM.html">Creating an email with Experience Manager and Campaign</a>: create an email content in Adobe Experience Manager and use it in an email in Adobe Campaign Standard.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_DeliveryBestPractices.html">Delivering with Adobe Campaign</a>: discover some of the best practices that can be used to deliver with Adobe Campaign, from creating and targeting to sending and monitoring.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_Deliverability.html">Optimizing your deliverability</a>: learn the key concepts and best practices related to deliverability as well as the tools offered by Adobe Campaign to optimize your deliveries.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="https://docs.campaign.adobe.com/doc/standard/getting_started/en/ACS_GDPR.html">General Data Protection Regulation</a>: discover the tools and functionalities that Adobe Campaign provides, as well as best practices, to help you become GDPR compliant.</p> </li>
  </ul>
  <p>Learn more about Adobe Campaign by checking the following use cases and examples:</p> 
  <ul>
   <li><p> <a href="../../automating/using/importing-data.md#example--import-workflow-template">Importing profiles</a>: import new client profiles with a workflow to your Adobe Campaign instance to update your database and to send emails.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../channels/using/key-steps-to-send-a-message.md">Key steps to send a message</a>: learn how to create and send messages step by step.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../integrating/using/abandonment-triggers-use-cases.md">Using Experience Cloud Triggers with Adobe Campaign</a>: send personalized emails to your customers following specific behaviors that were tracked by Adobe Analytics on your website.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../administration/using/use-case--users-e-security.md">Managing users and groups</a>: manage your users and groups to define their access to the interface.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../developing/using/key-steps.md">Adding or extending a resource</a>: learn how to create new resources or extend existing ones.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../automating/using/importing-data.md#example--import-workflow-template">Importing workflow template</a>: use import template to regularly import files with the same structure.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../channels/using/setting-up-a-double-opt-in-process.md">Setting up a double opt-in process</a>: learn how to send an email linked to a landing page to confirm a customer's subscription.</p> </li>
   <li><p> <a href="../../designing/using/example--email-personalization.md">Personalize an email</a>: personalize an email according to the customer's age.</p> </li>
  </ul>
